item.title: Prayer bpn6050 in Namibia
item.description: Ena rOye oro everukise, Ndjambi wandje, nu okuri zemburuka nayOve oko ondjamo komuinyo wandje. Okukara popezu nayOve ondjiri ondero yandje, nu orusuvero kOve onduri oupanga ounene. Otjari tjOye kwami ondjiri omberukiro no ndjamo indino nga kongaaruhe. Tjiri Oove Ndjambi wotjari, ngutjiwa avihe, Onongo yaavihe. (Source category: Otjiherero: OMBERUKIRO) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 6050)
